00:15:39,385 --> 00:15:39,960
President Gu!

315
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:40,780
President Gu!

316
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:42,000
President Gu!

317
00:15:42,370 --> 00:15:43,150
President Gu!

318
00:15:44,230 --> 00:15:44,790
President Gu!

