359
00:18:07,210 --> 00:18:11,410
You're just a servant.
Don't get ahead of yourself.

360
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:12,540
Ouyang.

361
00:18:15,210 --> 00:18:17,260
President Gu,
don't you hate this brat too?

362
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,640
I'll teach him a lesson for you.

363
00:18:27,210 --> 00:18:30,380
Why did you hit Lin? Don't go too far.

364
00:18:32,360 --> 00:18:35,590
