367
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,580
What's wrong?

368
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:57,650
President Gu,

369
00:18:59,070 --> 00:18:59,880
what's wrong?

370
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:03,740
President Gu,

371
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,330
you were there

372
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,700
