373
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:13,500
I remember this.

374
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:14,880
Yes.

375
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:17,910
I saved you.

376
00:19:19,190 --> 00:19:20,890
When you fell into the water
three months ago.

377
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:22,560
I thought you knew all along.

378
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,230
