383
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:45,450
Right?

384
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,170
So handsome.

385
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,240
President Gu.

386
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:51,720
There's even a crying scene.

387
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:57,970
I only lied to you

388
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:00,940
because

389
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,490
I wanted a place here,

390
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:10,570
