that place anymore today.

391
00:20:14,950 --> 00:20:16,170
President Gu, let's go.

392
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:28,540
That's crazy.

393
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:32,520
(Wanna find more interesting
stage live broadcast?)

394
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:34,400
(Follow @waytoyou2026 on Tiktok.
You'll get more surpring contents.)

395
00:20:35,930 --> 00:20:37,270
(Air thumbs-up)

396
00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:38,600
(Received)

397
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:40,370
Well done.

398
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:45,010
The challenge of acting
in just one scene is

399
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:46,630
