400
00:20:46,940 --> 00:20:50,180
but you have to pull the audience in.

401
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,430
So I set a standard for myself.

402
00:20:52,430 --> 00:20:53,160
Liking a show

403
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,050
