404
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:58,350
I really like these three.

405
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,930
(Loved this group's performance)
Great job.

406
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:03,760
Poom, you really fit this role.

407
00:21:04,390 --> 00:21:05,880
(Happy)
Because

408
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,170
