the full range of emotions.

411
00:21:12,230 --> 00:21:14,900
Like a rollercoaster.

412
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:18,630
I felt a lot from it.

413
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:22,760
Honestly, he played
the supporting villain

414
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:24,410
but still stole the show.

415
00:21:24,410 --> 00:21:27,400
(Scene stealer)

416
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:33,660
I really liked playing Ouyang.

417
00:21:33,970 --> 00:21:36,230
Because I studied him.

418
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:41,270
I read and understood his emotions,

419
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:43,070
