425
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,750
Deaw's gaze was great.

426
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:54,070
The three of them

427
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,710
made it very interesting.

428
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:57,980
U.Jay

429
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:02,900
