431
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,540
He looks great on camera.

432
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:08,530
Thank you.

433
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:11,960
I'd prefer if he spoke his own language.

434
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:15,670
If he spoke his mother tongue,

435
00:22:15,670 --> 00:22:19,560
