452
00:23:08,810 --> 00:23:09,590
President Gu.

453
00:23:09,940 --> 00:23:10,720
President Gu.

454
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:11,830
President Gu.

455
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:12,680
President Gu!

456
00:23:12,970 --> 00:23:13,630
President Gu.

457
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:17,530
President Gu!

458
