474
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:52,230
President Gu.

475
00:23:55,410 --> 00:23:56,110
President Gu!

476
00:23:56,610 --> 00:23:57,680
President Gu, sit up first.

477
00:23:59,060 --> 00:23:59,770
