482
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:23,690
50 million.

483
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,540
And leave President Gu alone.

484
00:24:25,540 --> 00:24:27,580
His eyes are so fierce.

485
00:24:27,660 --> 00:24:28,600
