490
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,310
100 million.

491
00:24:44,710 --> 00:24:46,550
Pack up and leave tonight.

492
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,410
He's the CEO.

493
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,470
I'll take the money and go.

494
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,360
