President Gu!

532
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,230
President Gu?

533
00:27:23,410 --> 00:27:24,030
President Gu.

534
00:27:26,120 --> 00:27:26,740
President Gu?

535
00:27:28,210 --> 00:27:28,850
President Gu,

536
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,150
are you alright?

537
00:27:33,660 --> 00:27:36,030
You were there
when I fell into the water.

538
00:27:40,470 --> 00:27:41,340
I remember this.

539
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:43,880
Yes, it was me.

540
00:27:44,210 --> 00:27:46,210
When you fell into the water
three months ago,

541
00:27:46,210 --> 00:27:47,590
I saved you.

542
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,590
I thought you knew all along.

543
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:54,030
He's feeling guilty.

544
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,310
So

545
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:58,000
it was you

546
00:27:58,650 --> 00:28:00,510
who pretended to be my savior

547
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:02,640
to earn my trust!

548
00:28:07,170 --> 00:28:10,020
So all the things I've done

549
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:14,470
