I even laughed watching it myself.

553
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:39,290
Barely passable. It wasn't great.

554
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:40,660
(Setting a goal)
I'll do better next time.

555
00:28:40,660 --> 00:28:43,410
We've actually filmed this kind
of drama before.

556
00:28:43,410 --> 00:28:46,030
