558
00:28:48,010 --> 00:28:50,000
But this time, it was all live.

559
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:52,830
So Chinese audiences
might find it a bit sudden.

560
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:54,110
Sudden.

561
00:28:54,740 --> 00:28:56,170
Sudden.

562
00:28:57,010 --> 00:28:58,800
(A CEO must maintain his dignity)

563
00:28:59,580 --> 00:29:00,820
(Staying silent)

564
