If your partner doesn't give you
enough freedom

1120
00:55:07,360 --> 00:55:10,500
or forces you to do things you dislike,

1121
00:55:10,910 --> 00:55:13,430
you'd rather walk away
from the relationship.

1122
00:55:15,270 --> 00:55:16,710
Okay. Next.

1123
00:55:16,920 --> 00:55:21,710
Dog represents loyalty and devotion.

1124
00:55:21,940 --> 00:55:24,780
If you chose dog as good news,

1125
00:55:24,780 --> 00:55:27,700
you want a partner
who loves you unconditionally,

1126
00:55:27,700 --> 00:55:32,040
stays by your side, and supports you.

1127
00:55:32,280 --> 00:55:33,000
That's all for dog.

1128
00:55:34,020 --> 00:55:35,510
But if you think dog brings bad news,

1129
00:55:35,510 --> 00:55:38,430
it means you
don't like unstable partners

1130
00:55:38,430 --> 00:55:40,810
who are overly suspicious,

1131
00:55:41,040 --> 00:55:42,430
constantly doubting,

1132
00:55:42,430 --> 00:55:46,640
or always trying hard to please others.

1133
00:55:48,840 --> 00:55:51,010
For today's animal-themed party,

1134
00:55:51,010 --> 00:55:52,540
we'll use games

1135
00:55:52,540 --> 00:55:54,780
to help everyone
understand your partners better.

1136
00:55:55,000 --> 00:55:57,720
We'll start with a simple game.

1137
00:55:58,010 --> 00:56:00,550
Please choose your partner for today.

1138
00:56:00,550 --> 00:56:03,350
This partner is just for today's game.

1139
00:56:03,350 --> 00:56:05,030
Not your partner for the week.

1140
00:56:05,030 --> 00:56:08,080
(Today's partner is only for the game)
No nationality restrictions this time.

1141
00:56:08,080 --> 00:56:08,680
Who should I pick?

1142
00:56:08,680 --> 00:56:10,240
(Hesitating)
We'll start the first game.

1143
00:56:14,280 --> 00:56:14,880
Okay.

1144
00:56:14,880 --> 00:56:15,640
Then.

1145
00:56:16,330 --> 00:56:17,460
Just for fun.

1146
00:56:17,460 --> 00:56:18,680
(Loves playing)
Just for fun.

1147
00:56:20,200 --> 00:56:21,650
The first game is called

1148
00:56:21,650 --> 00:56:23,220
(Animal Rhythm)
Animal Rhythm.

1149
00:56:23,220 --> 00:56:24,840
Let's do a demo round first.

1150
00:56:24,840 --> 00:56:26,000
(Hahaha)

1151
00:56:28,660 --> 00:56:31,980
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1152
00:56:32,520 --> 00:56:34,170
(Missed it)

1153
00:56:34,170 --> 00:56:35,850
Cow, cow, cat, cat,

1154
00:56:37,480 --> 00:56:38,880
Cat, meow...

1155
00:56:39,590 --> 00:56:40,810
(Laughing too hard to continue)

1156
00:56:42,380 --> 00:56:45,860
Sheep, sheep, frog, frog,
pig, wolf, pig, wolf.

1157
00:56:45,860 --> 00:56:46,640
(Correct)

1158
00:56:46,640 --> 00:56:47,610
It's quite simple.

1159
00:56:48,940 --> 00:56:52,160
Wolf, wolf, cow, cow,
cat, dog, cat, dog.

1160
00:56:52,160 --> 00:56:54,440
(Correct)

1161
00:56:55,350 --> 00:56:57,230
What's wolf? Awoo.

1162
00:57:00,260 --> 00:57:03,470
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1163
00:57:03,470 --> 00:57:06,830
Chicken, sheep, chicken, sheep,
frog, frog, wolf, dog.

1164
00:57:07,510 --> 00:57:09,470
(Success)
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1165
00:57:09,470 --> 00:57:10,940
What sound does a pig make? Wolf, pig...

1166
00:57:10,950 --> 00:57:13,490
(Laughing mid-game)

1167
00:57:13,990 --> 00:57:16,070
(Fail)

1168
00:57:16,570 --> 00:57:19,920
Sheep, dog, sheep, dog,
wolf, wolf, pig, frog.

1169
00:57:19,920 --> 00:57:21,280
(Success)

1170
00:57:22,580 --> 00:57:23,450
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1171
00:57:23,450 --> 00:57:27,250
Cat, pig, cat, pig,
dog, dog, frog, chicken.

1172
00:57:27,330 --> 00:57:28,700
(Success)
Great job!

1173
00:57:28,700 --> 00:57:29,820
Okay.

1174
00:57:29,820 --> 00:57:32,650
- Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!
- Is this it?

1175
00:57:33,170 --> 00:57:36,390
Cow, cow, cat, cat,
wolf, sheep, wolf, sheep.

1176
00:57:36,650 --> 00:57:38,590
(Success)

1177
00:57:38,590 --> 00:57:39,560
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1178
00:57:39,560 --> 00:57:42,880
Pig, pig, dog, dog,
frog, cat, frog, cat.

1179
00:57:42,880 --> 00:57:44,420
(Success)

1180
00:57:44,420 --> 00:57:46,090
Sheep, sheep, frog, frog...

1181
00:57:46,770 --> 00:57:49,460
(Missed the beat)
Not yet.

1182
00:57:49,460 --> 00:57:50,400
(Follow @waytoyou2026 on Tiktok.)
You jumped the beat.

1183
00:57:50,400 --> 00:57:51,730
(You'll get more surpring contents.)
Rappers can't jump the beat.

1184
00:57:51,870 --> 00:57:54,100
- Rappers can't jump the beat.
- How could a rapper jump the beat?

1185
00:57:54,220 --> 00:57:55,600
I don't have an in-ear monitor.

1186
00:57:55,600 --> 00:57:56,660
(Rapper who can't catch the beat)
Sorry.

1187
00:57:56,800 --> 00:57:58,640
1, 2, 3, go!

1188
00:57:58,640 --> 00:58:02,060
Wolf, wolf, cow, cow,
cat, dog, cat, dog.

1189
00:58:02,060 --> 00:58:03,610
(Success)
Nice!

1190
00:58:03,610 --> 00:58:05,150
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1191
00:58:05,150 --> 00:58:08,680
Chicken, sheep, chicken, sheep,
frog, frog, wolf, dog.

1192
00:58:08,680 --> 00:58:09,830
(Success)
Good job!

1193
00:58:09,830 --> 00:58:11,830
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1194
00:58:11,830 --> 00:58:12,980
Pig, cat...

1195
00:58:13,260 --> 00:58:13,920
Move.

1196
00:58:15,780 --> 00:58:16,630
No.

1197
00:58:18,260 --> 00:58:20,530
Pig, pig, pig, pig, pig, pig.

1198
00:58:20,530 --> 00:58:21,810
What are you saying?

1199
00:58:22,930 --> 00:58:24,860
