1200
00:58:24,860 --> 00:58:27,950
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1201
00:58:27,950 --> 00:58:31,120
Cat, pig, cat, pig,
dog, dog, frog, chicken.

1202
00:58:31,560 --> 00:58:33,290
(Success)

1203
00:58:33,290 --> 00:58:35,470
