1224
00:59:07,290 --> 00:59:10,070
Pig, dog, crow, chicken. 1, 2, 3, go!

1225
00:59:10,070 --> 00:59:11,440
Tron, Poom, Tron, Poom,

1226
00:59:11,440 --> 00:59:12,880
Cannon, Tai, Eugene, Kai.

1227
00:59:13,530 --> 00:59:15,200
