1246
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:01,010
(Me)

1247
01:00:02,460 --> 01:00:02,920
Eugene.

1248
01:00:02,920 --> 01:00:03,680
(Pippin & Eugene paired)

1249
01:00:03,680 --> 01:00:04,310
Poom.

1250
01:00:04,310 --> 01:00:05,790
